null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "In the Name of Allah, the most Gracious, the most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "(Shuru karta hu) Allah ke naam se Jo bada maher-baan nehaayat rahem karne waala hai.", "Urdu": "اللہ کے نام سے (شروع کرتا ہوں) جو بڑا مہربا ن نہایت رحم کرنے والا ہے۔", "RArabic": "BISMILLAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1011003, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah make me content with what You have decreed for me, conceal my faults give me good health so long as I live and forgive me and have mercy on me when I die. O Allah do not let me be involved in that which You have not decreed for me and what You have decreed for me, make it easy, available. O Allah reward my parents and all those who have favored me the best of rewards.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Paalne waale! Jo kuchh Tu ne diya hai us par qanaat karne ki taufiq ataa farma aur mere aiybo’n ko chhipa, aur mujhe salaamati ataa farma, aur meri maut se pehle mujhe bakhsh de. Mere gunah maaf farma aur apni rahmat mere shaamil'e haal farma. Baar'e Ilaaha! Jo kuchh mere liye muqaddar kar rakha hai us mein mujhe aazmaaish mein na daal aur jo kuchh mere muqaddar mein hai usey mere liye aasaani kar de. Parwardigaar! Waaledain aur jo bhi mujh par haq rakhta hai us ko beh-tareen jaza'e khair se nawaaz.", "Urdu": "اے پالنے والے:جو کچھ تو نے دیا ہے اس پر قناعت کرنے کی توفیق عطا فرما اور میرے عیوب کو چھپا، اورمجھے سلامتی عطا فرما، اور میری موت سے پہلے مجھے بخش دے۔ میرے گناہ معاف فرما اور اپنی رحمت میرے شامل حال فرما۔ بارالھا! جو کچھ میرے لئے مقدر کر رکھا ہے اس میں مجھے آزمائش میں نہ ڈال اور جو کچھ میرے مقدر میں ہے اسے میرے لئے آسان کردے۔ پروردگار! والدین اور جو بھی مجھ پر حق رکھتا ہے اس کو بہترین جزا خیرسے نواز۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA QANNE’NEE BEMAA RAZAQTANEE WAS TURNEE WA A’AFENEE ABADAN MAA ABQAYTANEE WAGH FIR LEE WAR HAMNEE EZAA TAWAFFAYTANEE, ALLAAHUMMA LAA TO’YENEE FEE TALABE MAA LAM TOQADDIR LEE WA MAA QADDARTAHU A’LAYYA FAJ-A’LHO MOYASSERAN SAHELAN. ALLAAHUMMA KAFE A’NNEE WAALEDAYYA, WA KULLA MAN LAHU NE’MATUN A’LAYYA KHAYRA MOKAAFAATIN.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰہُمَّ قَنِّعْنِیْ بِمَا رَزَقْتَنِیْ، وَاسْتُرْنِیْ وَعَافِنِیْ اَبَدًا مَّا اَبْقَیْتَنِیْ، وَاغْفِرْ لِیْ وَارْحَمْنِیْ اِذَا تَوَفَّیْتَنِیْ۔ اَللّٰہُمَّ لَا تُعْیِنِیْ فِیْ طَلَبِ مَا لَمْ تُقَدِّرْ لِیْ، وَمَا قَدَّرْتَہٗ عَلَیَّ فَاجْعَلْہُ مُیَسَّرًا سَہْلًا۔ اَللّٰہُمَّ کَافِ عَنِّیْ وَالِدَیَّ، وَکُلَّ مَنْ لَہٗ نِعْمَۃٌ عَلَیَّ خَیْرَ مُکَافَاۃٍ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1011004, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, free me for what You have created me and do not make me occupied in that which You have undertaken for me do not punish me while I seek Your forgiveness and do not deprive me while I ask from You. O Allah, make me humble make Your status great with me inspire me towards Your obedience and actions that please You and avoidance of that which angers You O most merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Baar'e Ilaaha! Jis maqsad ke liye mujhe paiyda kiya hai waqt usi jaanib mujhe mashghool (busy) rakh aur woh umoor jinki kifaalat ki zimme-daari khud Tu ne li hai un mein mashghool (busy) na farma. Mujhe azaab na de mai bakhshish ki talab-gaar hu. Mai Tujh se sawaal karti hu mujhe mehroom na rakh. Parwardigaar! Mere nafs ko zaleel o khwaar, apne maqaam o martaba ko mere nafs mein ziyadah farma aur mazeed yeh keh apni itaa’at ke saath saath aise amaal jo Tere pasandeeda hai kar ne ki taufiq ataa farma aur woh amaal jo Tere liye na-pasand hai un se mujhe dur rakh, ay beh-tareen rahem karne waale.", "Urdu": "بارالھا! جس مقصد کے لئے مجھے پیدا کیا ہے فقط اسی جانب مجھے مشغول رکھ اور وہ امور جن کی کفالت کی ذمہ داری خود تو نے لی ہے ان میں مشغول نہ فرما۔ مجھے عذاب نہ دے میں بخشش کی طلبگار ہوں۔ میں تجھ سے سوال کرتی ہوں مجھے محروم نہ رکھ۔ پروردگار! میرے نفس کو ذلیل و خوار، اپنے مقام و مرتبہ کو میرے نفس میں زیادہ فرما اور مزید یہ کہ اپنی اطاعت کے ساتھ ساتھ ایسے اعمال جو تیرے پسندیدہ ہیں کرنے کی توفیق عطا فرما اور وہ اعمال جو تیرے لئے ناپسند ہیں ان سے مجھے دور رکھ، اے بہترین رحم کرنے والے۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA FARRIGHNEE LEMAA KHALAQTANEE LAHU, WA LAA TASH-GHALNEE BEMAA TAKAFFALTA LEE BEHI. WALAA TO-A’ZZIBNEE WA ANAA AS-TAGHFEROKA, WA LAA TAHRIMNEE WA ANAA AS-ALOKA, ALLAAHUMMA ZALLIL NAFSEE FEE NAFSEE, WA A’ZZIM SHA-NAKA FEE NAFSEE, WA ALHIMNEE TA-A’TAKA, WAL A’MALA BEMAA YURZEEKA, WAT TAJANNOBA LEMAA YUSKHETOKA, YAA ARHAMAR RAAHEMEEN.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰہُمَّ فَرِّغْنِیْ لِمَا خَلَقْتَنِیْ لَہٗ، وَلَا تَشْغَلْنِیْ بِمَا تَکَفَّلْتَ لِیْ بِہٖ، وَلَا تُعَذِّبْنِیْ وَاَنَا اَسْتَغْفِرُکَ، وَلَا تَحْرِمْنِیْ وَاَنَا اَسْئَلُکَ۔ اَللّٰہُمَّ ذَلِّلْ نَفْسِیْ فِیْ نَفْسِیْ، وَعَظِّمْ شَانَکَ فِیْ نَفْسِیْ، وَاَلْہِمْنِیْ طَاعَتَکَ، وَالْعَمَلَ بِمَا یُرْضِیْکَ، وَالتَّجَنُّبَ لِمَا یُسْخِطُکَ، یَا اَرْحَمَ الرَّاحِمِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": 